<m0>At 80, housing director ready to slow down (--) maybe<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 1 IS .95 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS .423 INCHES<m2><ql>
